</taxonomicName>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="5B637615C3CE94E2B776820642170E3C" pageId="null" pageNumber="544" type="vernacular_names">
<paragraph id="8FDEF5630C22020D23E3B8BC49F2C10E" pageId="null" pageNumber="544">Chinesische Glyzine</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="9C3F6ECE5F33CA103600C5E203A6CCFF" lastPageNumber="543" pageId="null" pageNumber="544" type="description">
<paragraph id="BC64903C815F66FE5DD2B268EB6E14D0" lastPageNumber="543" pageId="null" pageNumber="544">
Bis 20 m hoch. Junge Zweige und 
<normalizedToken id="633676B2A832B0FE844AE01E2E108AD3" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="544">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
, 
<normalizedToken id="89A477BB6D4FAEE8262772C8C7455170" originalValue="Blütenstiele" pageId="null" pageNumber="544">Bluetenstiele</normalizedToken>
und Kelch kurz und seidig behaart. 
<normalizedToken id="A0104990276BAA412D2D1C3B6F47BAF8" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="544">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
gestielt, mit 7-13 
<normalizedToken id="29A4EE16D7DDEC8B5BA28FC2B3B0BBDE" originalValue="Teilblättern" pageId="null" pageNumber="544">Teilblaettern</normalizedToken>
; 
<normalizedToken id="CC3767287075981CD56F674B40E9F2A5" originalValue="Teilblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="544">Teilblaetter</normalizedToken>
4-8 cm lang, spitz, kurz gestielt. 
<normalizedToken id="8AA0E4BE329A62E3B15F5325F2E1C10F" originalValue="Blütenstände" pageId="null" pageNumber="544">Bluetenstaende</normalizedToken>
<pageBreakToken id="F2B8CFE04DE495DD844E0348BCD0126D" pageId="null" pageNumber="543" start="start">15</pageBreakToken>
-25 cm lang. 
<emphasis id="435CCF74B1AE982187535772D9255318" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="543">Krone blau bis violett</emphasis>
, angenehm duftend, 2-2,6 cm lang. Frucht 6-20 cm lang, 
<emphasis id="F230A6673A5F78B6512E0994FC00CD63" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="543">dicht samtig behaart.</emphasis>
- 
<normalizedToken id="83F494B3005B5EAD1A7C345373CF189F" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="543">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: 
<normalizedToken id="5DB3B73A93D683232B8ACDA13CDD8702" originalValue="Später" pageId="null" pageNumber="543">Spaeter</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="1017BC8B5E165D2C61C46BAF0E018780" originalValue="Frühling" pageId="null" pageNumber="543">Fruehling</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="A1A6270435BCF3CDB21070B64DB7C0E3" pageId="null" pageNumber="543">
<emphasis id="87BF3ED67132DE812C9D0863B04343C4" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="543">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="518DC8F0675F58F24DF337DBF8B59127" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="543">16:</emphasis>
Material unbekannter Herkunft (Roscoe aus Darlington und Wylie 1955).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="835491D65C22F2DF58489FA4F7F05BD3" pageId="null" pageNumber="543">
<emphasis id="C3C7DDD64B55D158076F74EC6E03DAB5" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="543">Standort.</emphasis>
Kollin. Lockere, sandige, kalkarme 
<normalizedToken id="4849DA37E2492AD530DAA5FCE3783AEA" originalValue="Böden" pageId="null" pageNumber="543">Boeden</normalizedToken>
in warmen und milden Lagen.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="604C3D4B3CF7A3BAC88913C9E965402F" pageId="null" pageNumber="543">
<emphasis id="1B2E5D75A964756252EC48F370726ADC" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="543">Verbreitung. Ostasiatische Pflanze.</emphasis>
- Im Gebiet oft in 
<normalizedToken id="474D299EC8F0D5BD02F81CAF100F0AB3" originalValue="Gärten" pageId="null" pageNumber="543">Gaerten</normalizedToken>
und an Mauern als Spalierstrauch in vielen Sorten angepflanzt, nur sehr selten verwildert.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
